        "description": "Execute a specific BioMate workflow on BioMate cloud with explicit parameters. Returns a run_id immediately. If stream=true, also emits progress notifications until the run terminates (same events as biomate_session). Use biomate_session instead when the user gave you a natural-language goal.",
